				\begin{document}$$J={J}_{0}[exp(\frac{q(V-J{R}_{S})}{nkT})-1]$$\end{document}where2J0∝exp(−EakT)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
